Package project.farm

Class CityFarmerMenu

java.lang.Object
project.farm.CityFarmerMenu
public class CityFarmerMenu
extends java.lang.Object
A class with static methods that can be called from social magnet menu to display farm options.

  • Method Details

    • displayFarmHeader

      public static void displayFarmHeader​(java.lang.String type, UserProfile user)
      This is a static helper method to help display the standard starting interface of any farm sub screens.
      Parameters:
      type - Type of sub screen, goes by "case" + 1-5, or "main"
      user - the user object thats currently using the application

    • readOptions

      public static void readOptions​(UserProfile user)
      This is a static method that displays the farm main menu. Called from ProfileMenu only.

      This is the primary screen of City Farmer. This method redirects requests to any sub screens in City Farmer by calling the associated methods.

      Parameters:
      user - UserProfile object of current user

    • viewFarmMenu

      public static java.lang.String viewFarmMenu​(UserProfile user)
      This method creates a ctrl of the current user object and displays his farmland.
      Parameters:
      user - UserProfile object of current user
      Returns:
      Redirection string with the value of 'main' / 'farm' / ''. If 'main', returns from this screen and displays ProfileMenu. Else, stays in this screen.

    • accessFriendMenu

      public static java.lang.String accessFriendMenu​(UserProfile user)
      This method creates a ctrl of the current user object and displays his friends.
      Parameters:
      user - UserProfile object of current user
      Returns:
      Redirection string with the value of either a friend's username or an empty screen. Helps to redirect the next method to the correct farm screen.

    • accessFriendFarmMenu

      public static java.lang.String accessFriendFarmMenu​(UserProfile user, java.lang.String friendUsername)
      This method creates a ctrl of the current user object and displays the selected friend's farm.
      Parameters:
      user - UserProfile object of current user
      friendUsername - the username of the friend whose farm should be displayed
      Returns:
      Redirection string with the value of 'main' / 'farm' / ''. If 'main', returns from this screen and displays ProfileMenu. Else, stays in this screen.
